HEADWORD: Mullock
<hw>Mul"lock</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Mull</er>
dirt: cf. Scot. <ets>mulloch</ets>, <ets>mulock</ets>, crumb.
⟦root⟧108.]</ety> <def>Rubbish; refuse; dirt.</def>
